translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_915dfc04:
    # mc "Damn, this place is a mess!"
    mc "Sial, tempat ini berantakan!"

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_9413d727:
    # mc "It'll take me a whole day to clean this place!"
    mc "Aku butuh seharian penuh untuk membersihkan tempat ini!"

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_130f4b51:
    # mc "Now I see why Igor was so angry whenever I came to talk to him."
    mc "Sekarang aku mengerti kenapa Igor selalu marah setiap kali aku datang bicara dengannya."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_5d99ef7a:
    # "There you are."
    "Ternyata kau di sini."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_98f48f28:
    # mc "I'm exactly where I should be, no?"
    mc "Aku tepat berada di tempat yang seharusnya, bukan?"

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_21939bcb:
    # "I warn you for the last time. You'd better not mess with me."
    "Aku memperingatkanmu untuk terakhir kalinya. Sebaiknya kau jangan macam-macam denganku."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_9e464f66:
    # mc "You wanted me to give her the pendant, I did that. What's the problem?"
    mc "Kau ingin aku memberikan liontin itu padanya, dan sudah kulakukan. Apa masalahnya?"

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_6af1148e:
    # "…."
    "...."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_594ed906:
    # "You will pay for your insolence!"
    "Kau akan membayar kelancanganmu!"

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_a7065b22:
    # "I promise you that."
    "Aku berjanji padamu."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_eef34086:
    # mc "Hey, are you threatening me?"
    mc "Hei, kau mengancamku?"

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_51560bc8:
    # "I'm just warning you."
    "Aku hanya memperingatkanmu."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_8cab029b:
    # "I'll be constantly watching you now, [mc]."
    "Mulai sekarang aku akan terus mengawasimu, [mc]."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_ce9285e1:
    # "You'd better not skip a single working day at the park..."
    "Sebaiknya kau jangan melewatkan satu hari kerja pun di taman..."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_6b50033c:
    # "You'd better not be seen in a suspicious place..."
    "Sebaiknya kau jangan terlihat di tempat mencurigakan..."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_a9572a8e:
    # "You'd better not hang out with a suspicious group of people..."
    "Sebaiknya kau jangan bergaul dengan sekelompok orang mencurigakan..."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_9fc47a56:
    # "Or cross the road in a wrong place..."
    "Atau menyeberang jalan di tempat yang salah..."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_a4ad07af:
    # mc "He-heh! You sound like my mommy."
    mc "He-heh! Kau terdengar seperti ibuku."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_f4adfa41:
    # "…."
    "...."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_0bea6f75:
    # "See you soon."
    "Sampai jumpa lagi."

translate indonesian ep45_milf_51_2_af5fa993:
    # mc "Good day to you too, officer!"
    mc "Selamat siang juga, Pak Polisi!"
